{
  "title": "Sour Adventurous Pepper Cornish Pastry",
  "description": "A savory pastry filled with a shaggy mixture of sautéed peppers and spices, wrapped in a gluten-free friendly cornish-pasty crust. Perfect for adventurous eaters looking for a flavorful and tangy snack.",
  "cuisine": "british",
